        public CoverageParams(int startPosition,
              int endPosition,
              int zoomLevel)
        Create new coverage parameters
        Parameters:
        startPosition - The starting position in the chromosome to search for the variant, can be any number within the range of the chromosome. No default value, must be specified and must be an integer.
        endPosition - The ending position in the chromosome to search for the variant, can be any number within the range of the chromosome. No default value, must be specified and must be an integer
        zoomLevel - granularity per bin
